        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued April 24 at 11:58PM CDT until April 25 at 12:15AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1158 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Codman, or 10
miles east of Pampa, moving southeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Codman.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
